{"type": "article", "id": 50907, "title": "把动物脸画在碗底，吃完心情不错｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-07T23:15:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 10665, "name": "品牌设计"}, {"id": 4436, "name": "字体设计"}, {"id": 48258, "name": "KEEGO"}, {"id": 48259, "name": "Kasthall"}, {"id": 48260, "name": "Zero Chroma"}, {"id": 48261, "name": "Oh Yeah Studio"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 41489, "name": "Case Studyo"}, {"id": 4011, "name": "Jean Jullien"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 128, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180307213949TVX5OZriPFC7jzR0.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Animal Bowls by Jean Jullien</h3><p>在插画领域颇受好评的插画家 Jean Jullien，最近与当代艺术家作品出版商、制造商 Case Studyo 合作推出了陶瓷餐具系列 Animal Bowls，这是他之前推出的餐盘系列 Face Plates 的后续版本。</p><p>这四个手工制作的彩色陶瓷碗底，是 Jean Julien 创作的标志性风格的动物脸，包括狗、猫、鱼和青蛙，鼓励使用者卸下伪装，不用太在乎刻板的餐桌礼仪，像动物一样尽情享用美食，甚至会放下羞涩的一面舔舔碗底。售价 39 欧元，<a href=\"https://casestudyo.myshopify.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214019NfYrwi3luWSTJM4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654545\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214019fSBjw96o2kK1aFC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.939091\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214019KJQRBe3XuIHz4yO7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214020JFzD5ws287eBEpYK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.939091\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214020xbwnK3RoCBGJmrsy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.850909\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214022eyUdZbzxnQCWLlIi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.939091\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214024zINtB6nD4KeE0mMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.939091\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://casestudyo.myshopify.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Case Studyo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>New “quintessentially British” 10p Coins</h3><p>英国皇家铸币局推出了 26 款 10 便士的图案设计，以英文字母 A 至 Z 作顺序，每个字母代表一个有英国特色的名词，并以图像表现出来。例如 A 代表著名雕塑作品《北方天使》（Angel of the North）、F 代表炸鱼薯条，N 代表英国国家卫生事务局（NHS），B 就印上电影角色《占士邦》的代号“007”。</p><p>英国皇家铸币局这次推出新设计是为了通过表达英国人的生活方式，尝试引起民间的收藏硬币热潮。每款硬币可以 2 英镑的价格购得，但以银铸造的“收藏家版本”，每枚售价则为 35 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214207JUZfpXVakqSRcNhT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214207KzNLDefXg1YTctuM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214207Xp8Pag6kviVxAlsW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214207BR1UJAHWk7uCKp8n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.998619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214208pL6GQgIeBZK5WbjN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214208geuCGaTBb5lOVPEZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803072142098VuYygdaLtkXGQMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214209SWVDoFO9hs8vBtj6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/news/the-royal-mint-quintessentially-british-10p-coin-graphic-design-050318\" rel=\"nofollow\">It’s Nice That</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Custom Typeface by Oh Yeah Studio for Nike</h3><p>在对奥斯陆门店进行重新设计时，耐克邀请当地的平面设计师，Oh Yeah Studio 的创始人 Hans Christian Øren 创作了一套字体，试图传达奥斯陆的城市精神。设计师希望能够结合耐克、体育以及奥斯陆三者之间的关系，创造出能够体现三者之间联系的视觉语言，最终确定了 lines of sport 的主题。</p><p>给予他灵感的是当地地标性的 Bislett 体育场，跑道的样式成为了这一系列字母的设计基础，既传达出耐克作为运动品牌的特征，又表现了北欧的极简主义。这一系列字体现在已在奥斯陆门店的徽标、海报、各种图片、墙纸以及装置中更新。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214311FBNEeKwq1fSbTI6V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654696\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214311jQt4sExYBnpvuIaK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563536\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214311cPnqJCeibg8ZxUAS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563536\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214311vwQ71KXhYBHWIgJP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.654696\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214311CrmTYiyJGtXBIWHS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563536\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214312vDj1X9cy6nZHUfEm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563536\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214312f0y2Y7ULnirbpF5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563536\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.ohyeahstudio.no/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Oh Yeah Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>HALO EFFECT First Handsfree 4-Mount Smartphone Kit by Brian Le Gette</h3><p>手机配件品牌 Zero Chroma 最近在众筹网站 IndieGoGo 上推出了一款解放双手的智能手机套件，当你需要拎箱子、拿重物或者任何需要双手的场合，HALO EFFECT 都是一种解决方案。它包括一个通用基座，可以插入三个不同的安装座，分别适用于驾驶、跑步骑车以及工作场合。早鸟价 39 美元，<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/halo-effect-first-handsfree-4-mount-smartphone-kit-design#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=j0600akpfue&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214404YRj7VqfKzvW0SH31.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666187\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214404YR1y9FWsEH5wnag3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667626\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214405ToAjvlHpYfWQ1EgG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667626\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214405DFmzR0KP6GWvtSLY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667626\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214405ho7Hs0uAU1nSEWyz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667626\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214405Fxv6kbcto0rZzDfH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214406lQMAG4Na0tkOeXi2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667626\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Four New Rugs by Kasthall</h3><p>在今年的斯德哥尔摩设计周期间，瑞典地毯品牌 Kasthall 推出了四款新地毯，是由中央圣马丁学院的毕业生和 Kasthall 的内部设计师 Maja Johansson Starander 合作设计的。</p><p>Freyja 是一款手工簇绒地毯，簇绒毛圈在不同的高度处留下未切割的部分以形成不平坦的表面，有点像羊皮地毯。</p><p>Gabrielle 是由亚麻和羊毛纱制成的梭织地毯，设计灵感来自复古纺织品，有精心制作的细节，尤其是刺绣。纱线织出不规则的垂直条纹，产生不对称感，提供三种不同的图案和颜色可供选择。</p><p>Katja 的特色在于切割出了两个不同的高度，创造出抽象的有机模式。</p><p>Diamond 则使用了一种被称为 over-driving 的新的编织技术，将每一层混合起来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214501dUiSGEwPXxzuO5mc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214501K0Sra2TY1nHdP4xh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803072145028RCQThW4azyfEtor.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214501MYkzS0sULpwHbfe7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214503xE8e1u2gpQbOoUPi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214504B04Huqwl3F1APQbG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214504JS12f0XNd5qmi6RP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/sff18-kasthall-launches-new-celebrates-old-embraces-different/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>World's First Squeezable Metal Bottle by Keg</h3><p>很多时候，运动员都需要一个可挤压的水杯，可以单手、快速、精确地饮水。但目前市面上所有可挤压的水杯都是塑料制成的。</p><p>两年前，奥地利体育用品品牌 KEEGO 开始研发可挤压水杯。尝试多次后，设计师发现了一种合适的材料弹性钛，可代替塑料，并找到合作生产商将其量产。瓶子的可挤压性基于材料的创新性使用，设计时也考虑到了人的握感，以及如何更容易挤压。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=f0601m5feeu&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214546V6g8eEtya9xhF7Q3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214546iY7zpJvnIxRmuZ1a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214546Nbd6ZoLVvagz1w2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214547ItTX4FhEJyONxzuZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562347\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214547bcTaqz5Q8BtZv4UE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180307214547YynWEFB0H4uMvz3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803072145481fLuF5GRhirgbIks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}